  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Willam Whistler</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\nPrince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Aenys I)\">Aegon Targaryen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/43_AC\" title=\"43 AC\">43&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Gods_Eye\" title=\"Gods Eye\">Gods Eye</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Willam Whistler</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willam_Whistler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Willam supported Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Aenys_I)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Aenys I)\">Aegon the Uncrowned</a> when he rebelled against his uncle, <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor the Cruel</a>. Aegon and Willam both died in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_Beneath_the_Gods_Eye\" title=\"Battle Beneath the Gods Eye\">Battle Beneath the Gods Eye</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/43_AC\" title=\"43 AC\">43&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Willam_Whistler&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403133503\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.058 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.232 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 435/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10467/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4181/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 535/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 595/5000000 bytes\n